<p>The linear relationship betweand two quantitative variables is examined through a single linear regression analysis in a sample of 30 people. The researcher wants to maintain an alpha level of 0.01.</p>
<p>Which critical <em>t</em> value belongs to a two-sided test for the linear relationship?</p>
</p>]]></text>
